5%E0%A5%87%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1752271300284862566%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2030%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIs%20this%20the%20result%20of%20compromising%20with%20Godse%20for%20power%3F%20Congress%20had%20fought%20against%20this%20thinking%20before%20and%20will%20fight%20now%20too%3B%20and%20will%20ensure%20social%20justice%20and%20equality%20in%20the%20true%20sense!%20K%20C.%20Tyagi%20should%20immediately%20apologise%20to%20Congress%20President%20Shri%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3ETyagi%20said%20that%20his%20statement%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cpoliticised%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20he%20was%20only%20referring%20to%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20being%20%E2%80%9Ctreated%20as%20untouchables%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20other%20regional%20parties%20prior%20to%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20of%20stitching%20together%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20was%20%E2%80%9Cuntouchable%E2%80%9D%20for%20its%20alliance%20parties%20and%20for%20regional%20parties.%20They%20were%20not%20talking%20to%20them.%20Was%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20talking%20to%20them%3F%20Was%20Shiv%20Sena%20talking%3F%20Was%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20talking%3F%20%E2%80%98Acchoot%E2%80%99%20does%20not%20mean%20Dalit.%20They%20politicise%20everything.%20What%20I%20meant%20was%20that%20nobody%20was%20ready%20to%20talk%20to%20them%2C%20they%20were%20being%20treated%20as%20%E2%80%98acchoot%E2%80%99.%20Now%20they%20are%20asking%20for%20an%20apology%20to%20Kharge%20and%20raising%20questions%20on%20us%20not%20being%20a%20social%20justice%20party.%20I%20said%20they%20were%20being%20treated%20as%20untouchables.%20What%20is%20wrong%20in%20what%20I%20said%3F%20No%20one%20was%20ready%20to%20touch%20them.%20No%20one%20was%20ready%20to%20speak%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3ETyagi%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthird%20rate%20antics%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmanipulations%E2%80%9D%20that%20led%20to%20the%20JD(U)%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-kumar-india-alliance-exit%5C%22%3Eultimate%20exit%20from%20the%20alliance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20while%20the%20party%20had%20no%20roadmap%20for%20seat%20sharing%20it%20wanted%20to%20grab%20big%20posts%20in%20the%20alliance.%20While%20Nitish%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20switching%20sides%20frequently%20in%20self%20interest%2C%20Tyagi%20said%20that%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20is%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20unlike%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20JD(U)%20is%20able%20to%20work%20with%20the%20BJP%20despite%20ideological%20differences%20on%20certain%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20the%20full%20interview%20below.%20Some%20answers%20have%20been%20edited%20lightly%20for%20length.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJD(U)%E2%80%99s%20alliance%20with%20the%20RJD%20in%20Bihar%20was%20ended%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20even%20though%20there%20was%20speculation%20in%20the%20media%20for%20the%20past%20few%20weeks.%20How%20was%20this%20decision%20taken%20and%20was%20this%20a%20sudden%20decision%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20left%20the%20NDA%2C%20we%20had%2016%20MPs%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20the%20chief%20minister.%20We%20did%20not%20make%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20RJD%20because%20of%20any%20political%20ambitions%2C%20or%20for%20the%20post%20of%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Due%20to%20the%20efforts%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20was%20held%20in%20Patna.%20This%20was%20the%20time%20when%20Kejriwal%2C%20Akhilesh%2C%20Mamata%20and%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20were%20maintaining%20a%20distance%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20non-Congress%2C%20non-BJP%20alternative.%20Exactly%201.5%20years%20ago%20during%20the%20Devi%20Lal%20Jayanti%20in%20Hisar%2C%20Nitish%20was%20there%20and%20so%20was%20Tejashwi%20and%20I%20was%20also%20present.%20He%20said%20that%20without%20Congress%20any%20option%20will%20not%20be%20successful.%20We%20need%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20Congress%20as%20it%20is%20a%20big%20party.%20And%20he%20appealed%20to%20all%20leaders%2C%20he%20came%20to%20Delhi%20along%20with%20Lalu%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Tejashwi%20and%20met%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%20But%20in%20the%20last%201.5%20years%2C%20the%20Congress%20not%20only%20tried%20to%20take%20over%20the%20big%20posts%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20but%20had%20no%20roadmap%20for%20seat%20sharing%20arrangements%20or%20joint%20campaigning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20meeting%20in%20three%20months.%20Nitish%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20then%20became%20active%20again%20and%20then%20we%20met%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai.%20And%20then%20after%201.5%20years%20we%20met%20at%20the%20Ashoka%20Hotel%20in%20Delhi%20(in%20December).%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20and%20Lalu%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20said%20on%20various%20occasions%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20brought%20this%20alliance%20together%20so%20naturally%20he%20should%20be%20made%20the%20convenor.%20But%20Nitish%20announced%20on%20several%20occasions%20that%20he%20is%20not%20a%20contender%20for%20this%20post.%20In%20Mumbai%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20PM%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20after%20we%20cross%20the%20272-mark%20will%20we%20decide.%20One%20day%20before%20the%20meeting%20at%20Ashoka%20Hotel%20(in%20Delhi)%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20came%20to%20Delhi%20and%20met%20Kejriwal%20for%20tea%20and%20then%20both%20announced%20together%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20face%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20But%20during%20the%20meeting%20the%20next%20day%20she%20suddenly%20got%20up%20and%20without%20taking%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20suggestion%20she%20suggested%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20name%20(for%20chairperson)%20and%20Kejriwal%20supported%20her.%20Kharge%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20gracefully%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20Congress%20party%20leadership%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20anything%20except%20to%20grab%20power%20by%20climbing%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20regional%20parties.%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20MP%2C%20Himachal%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Assam%20and%20Telangana-these%20are%20their%20areas.%20There%20they%20decided%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20seat%20sharing%20with%20any%20party.%20In%20UP%20they%20have%20one%20MP%20but%20want%2020%20seats%2C%20in%20Bihar%20they%20have%201%20MP%20but%20they%20want%2010%20seats%2C%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20they%20have%208%20MPs%20but%20want%2015%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryday%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury%20(Congress%20MP%20from%20West%20Bengal)%20has%20been%20asking%20for%20Mamata%20Banerjee%E2%80%99s%20government%20to%20be%20finished%20but%20they%20also%20want%2010%20seats%20there.%20In%20Maharashtra%20they%20have%201%20MP%20but%20want%2025%20seats.%20So%20they%20want%20to%20finish%20regional%20parties%20and%20fire%20from%20their%20shoulders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20and%20Akhilesh%20have%20also%20urged%20them%20to%20finish%20seat%20sharing%20talks%20on%20various%20occasions.%20Congress%20does%20not%20know%20how%20big%20an%20organisation%20BJP%20is%20and%20how%20widely%20they%20have%20spread%20out%20at%20the%20village%20booth%20level%20conducting%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20our%20end%2C%20apart%20from%20intrigue%20and%20manipulation%20no%20other%20work%20has%20been%20done.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20from%20our%20alliance%20partner%2C%20two%20to%20three%20ministers%20were%20engaged%20in%20making%20statements%20about%20how%20the%20party%20should%20be%20anti-Hindu%2C%20anti-Ram.%20They%20kept%20making%20statements%20against%20Ram%2C%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20and%20on%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Pran%20Pratishtha.%20All%20this%20ensured%20that%20it%20was%20advantage%20BJP%20and%20disadvantage%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20one%20goes%20(to%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha)%20or%20not%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20their%20personal%20faith.%20There%20is%20no%20point%20in%20making%20statements%20against%20who%E2%80%99s%20going.%20So%20we%20were%20tired%20of%20all%20this%20and%20decided%20to%20end%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FebfhxBHWx4Y%3Fsi%3DUtke7XsXQRbDeq8V%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20have%20earlier%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20conspiracy%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20not%20give%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20convenor%20or%20chairperson%E2%80%99s%20post%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20Are%20you%20holding%20the%20Congress%20solely%20responsible%20or%20do%20you%20see%20a%20hand%20by%20the%20other%20parties%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20gave%20birth%20to%20this%20conspiracy.%20Just%20look%20at%20the%20statements%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20making%20even%20today%20in%20Bihar.%20He%20is%20saying%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20did%20not%20want%20to%20conduct%20the%20caste%20survey%20and%20he%20did%20it%20under%20pressure%20from%20us.%20Why%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20Congress%20conducted%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20any%20state%20that%20it%20is%20in%20power%3F%20Congress%20was%20also%20against%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20and%20opposed%2027%25%20reservation%20for%20backward%20castes%20and%20also%20brought%20down%20the%20VP%20Singh%20government.%20His%20own%20father%20(Rajiv%20Gandhi)%20in%20a%201.5%20hour%20speech%20drank%20water%203%20times%20and%20said%20there%20should%20not%20be%20caste%20based%20reservations.%20So%20how%20a%20big%20leader%20like%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20says%20things%20like%20this%20is%20beyond%20our%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20referred%20to%20the%20Congress%20as%20an%20achoot%20party.%20The%20Congress%20has%20responded%20to%20your%20statement%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20a%20party%20that%20talks%20about%20social%20justice%20is%20using%20such%20words.%20How%20would%20you%20respond%20to%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20was%20%E2%80%9Cuntouchable%E2%80%9D%20for%20its%20alliance%20parties%20and%20for%20regional%20parties.%20They%20were%20not%20talking%20to%20them.%20Was%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20talking%20to%20them%3F%20Was%20Shiv%20Sena%20talking%3F%20Was%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20talking%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Acchoot%E2%80%99%20does%20not%20mean%20Dalit.%20They%20politicise%20everything.%20What%20I%20meant%20was%20that%20nobody%20was%20ready%20to%20talk%20to%20them%2C%20they%20were%20being%20treated%20as%20%E2%80%98acchoot%E2%80%99.%20Now%20they%20are%20asking%20for%20an%20apology%20to%20Kharge%20and%20raising%20questions%20on%20us%20not%20being%20a%20social%20justice%20party.%20I%20said%20they%20were%20being%20treated%20as%20untouchables.%20What%20is%20wrong%20in%20what%20I%20said%3F%20No%20one%20was%20ready%20to%20touch%20them.%20No%20one%20was%20ready%20to%20speak%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20question%20that%20is%20being%20raised%20now%20is%20that%20as%20you%20yourself%20said%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20working%20hard%20to%20build%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20But%20after%20difficulties%20came%20up%20within%20the%20alliance%2C%20he%20left%20the%20alliance%20and%20went%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20very%20party%20he%20was%20working%20against%20%E2%80%93%20how%20should%20one%20see%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20worked%20with%20them%20before%20as%20well.%20The%20birth%20of%20our%20social%20justice%20struggle%20has%20been%20against%20the%20Congress%20itself.%20Our%20political%20ancestors%2C%20Jayprakash%20Narayan%2C%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20they%20have%20fought%20against%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20We%20have%20gone%20to%20jail%20with%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Jan%20Sangh%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20first%20three%20governments%20were%20with%20the%20BJP%20itself.%20Yes%2C%20we%20have%20some%20differences%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20like%20Article%20370%2C%20Babri%20Masjid-Ram%20Janmabhoomi.%20Now%20as%20far%20as%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20disagree%20with%20them%20on%20that%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20how%20will%20you%20work%20with%20them%20with%20these%20disagreements%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESee%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20matter%20has%20been%20settled%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Article%20370%20we%20have%20already%20protested.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20the%20UCC%20we%20will%20give%20our%20suggestions%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20push%20it%20in%20haste.%20Speak%20to%20all%20the%20stakeholders%2C%20all%20religious%20minorities%20and%20state%20chief%20ministers.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20treat%20such%20sensitive%20matters%20in%20haste.%20We%20will%20give%20these%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJD(U)%20has%20struggled%20for%20social%20justice%20and%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20has%20conducted%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar.%20But%20now%20you%20have%20joined%20hands%20with%20a%20party%20that%20has%20never%20taken%20a%20clear%20position%20on%20the%20caste%20survey%20and%20did%20not%20support%20the%20exercise%20either.%20Will%20this%20alliance%20be%20a%20setback%20to%20the%20JD(U)%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20for%20social%20justice%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20a%20party%20born%20out%20of%20the%20struggle%20for%20social%20justice.%20Our%20leader%20Lohia%20spoke%20about%20reservations%20for%20backward%20castes%2C%20women.%20In%201978%20our%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarpoori-thakur-bharat-ratna-bjp-rjd-modi-lalu%5C%22%3EKarpoori%20Thakur%3C%2Fa%3E%20brought%20the%20Mungeri%20Lal%20commission.%20V.P.%20Singh%20implemented%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20country%20knows%20that%20a%20caste%20survey%20has%20been%20conducted%20only%20by%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20in%20Bihar%20and%20nowhere%20else.%20We%20have%20always%20maintained%20that%20the%20backward%20castes%20need%20to%20know%20their%20economic%20social%20status%20in%20the%2075th%20year%20of%20independence.%20And%20the%20results%20that%20came%20out%20were%20shocking.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20increased%20the%20reservations%20in%20the%20state%20and%20worked%20towards%20their%20economic%20empowerment.%20So%20we%20have%20been%20the%20pioneers%20of%20social%20justice%2C%20why%20will%20we%20step%20back%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20credit%20war%20is%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20media%20between%20JD(U)%20and%20the%20RJD%2C%20with%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20referring%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-strong-says-opposition-block-as-nitish-kumar-rejoins-hands-with-nda%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Ethake%20huye%20mukhyamantri%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20and%20claiming%20credit%20for%20the%20promise%20to%20provide%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthis-election-season-who-gets-to-take-the-credit-for-jobs-and-reservation-in-bihar%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20How%20do%20you%20see%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20not%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20making%20personal%20remarks%20against%20any%20senior%20politician.%20His%20father%20is%20also%20tired%20and%20sick.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20such%20language%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20who%20has%20held%20such%20a%20senior%20post%20and%20worked%20with%20us%20in%20the%20past%20should%20not%20do%20so%20either.%20Secondly%2C%20all%20parties%20promised%20jobs%20in%20their%20election%20manifestos%20and%20so%20did%20the%20RJD.%20It%20was%20the%20RJD-JD(U)%20government%20that%20was%20headed%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%20that%20finally%20gave%20the%20jobs.%20If%20they%20try%20to%20take%20credit%2C%20we%20can%20do%20so%20too%20but%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%20know%20what%20the%20truth%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComing%20back%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20if%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20made%20convenor%20then%20would%20the%20JD(U)%20have%20stayed%20in%20the%20alliance%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20just%20about%20being%20the%20convenor%20or%20chairperson%2C%20he%20had%20already%20declined%20these%20posts%20on%20several%20occasions.%20He%20formed%20the%20alliance%20and%20he%20wanted%20the%20alliance%20to%20be%20successful.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20that%20was%20creating%20problems.%20Now%20look%20at%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20they%20(Congress)%20have%20one%20MP%20but%20want%2020%20seats.%20And%20this%20is%20the%20case%20everywhere.%20In%20Bengal%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury%20wants%20to%20end%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20now%20and%20now%20Mamata%20has%20said%20there%20will%20be%20no%20alliance%20in%20Bengal.%20So%20it%20is%20not%20just%20us.%20No%20party%20wants%20to%20work%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20see%20a%20future%20at%20all%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20will%20it%20be%20able%20to%20make%20an%20impact%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20lost%20that%20opportunity.%20When%20we%20held%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20momentum%20was%20in%20our%20favour%20and%20we%20were%20ready%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20on%20400%20plus%20seats.%20But%20due%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20third%20rate%20antics%20and%20manipulation%2C%20not%20just%20us%2C%20even%20the%20SP%20is%20looking%20at%20them%20with%20mistrust%20and%20so%20is%20Mamata.%20The%20seat%20sharing%20arrangement%20is%20also%20not%20set%20with%20the%20RJD.%20The%20same%20situation%20is%20in%20Maharashtra%20where%20they%20have%20only%20one%20MP%20but%20want%20no%20less%20than%2020-22%20seats.%20So%20the%20Congress%20is%20stuck%20in%20its%20old%20ways%20and%20syndrome.%20This%20was%20the%20time%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20look%20to%20survive.%20But%20instead%20of%20survival%2C%20it%20started%20fighting%20for%20revival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinally%2C%20will%20the%20BJP-JD(U)%20alliance%20be%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20only%20or%20will%20you%20fight%20together%20in%20the%202025%20Bihar%20elections%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20long%20experience%20of%20working%20with%20the%20BJP.%20We%20have%20had%20some%20differences%20with%20them%20on%20matters%20of%20princple.%20But%20we%20had%20no%20problem%20working%20with%20them.%20When%20our%20numbers%20were%20less%2C%20they%20made%20our%20leader%20the%20chief%20minister.%20And%20in%202014%20we%20had%202%20MPs%2C%20they%20allowed%20our%20candidates%20to%20fight%20on%2017%20seats%20and%20we%20won%2016%20of%20those.%20So%20that%20attitude%20is%20not%20there%20with%20the%20Congress.%20While%20we%20may%20not%20differ%20with%20the%20Congress%20ideologically%20as%20such%2C%20their%20attitude%20towards%20work%20is%20the%20problem%20and%20is%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20any%20regional%20party.%20Any%20regional%20party%20that%20has%20been%20born%20has%20been%20born%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20Congress%20whether%20it%20is%20SP%2C%20BSP%2C%20TMC%20or%20anyone.%20They%20want%20to%20end%20regional%20parties%20and%20slowly%20the%20entire%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20disintegrate%20with%20all%20regional%20parties%20leaving%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20(JDU-BJP)%20is%20a%20permanent%20alliance%2C%20both%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706763441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01101931%2FKC-Tyagi.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Facchoot-doesnt-mean-dalit-congress-politicises-everything-jdus-k-c-tyagi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Responding%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20charge%20of%20belying%20its%20own%20social%20justice%20politics%2C%20JD(U)%E2%80%99s%20political%20advisor%20and%20national%20spokesperson%20K.C.%20Tyagi%20said%20that%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20being%20%E2%80%9Ctreated%20as%20untouchables%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20other%20regional%20parties%20prior%20to%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20of%20stitching%20together%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Facchoot-doesnt-mean-dalit-congress-politicises-everything-jdus-k-c-tyagi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reliance%2C%20Bodhi%20Tree%20discuss%2060%25%20stake%20in%20Disney%20India%20merger%20talks%3A%20Rpts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706763083000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F23%2Ffull%2F1682249330-2022.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-bodhi-tree-discuss-60-stake-in-disney-india-merger-talks-rpts-124020100188_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Under%20the%20deal%2C%20Viacom18%2C%20the%20broadcast%20division%20of%20Ambani's%20Reliance%20Industries%20will%20merge%20with%20Disney%20India%20businesses%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%2