0but%20civilian%20infrastructure%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20see%20from%20where%20they%20position%20themselves%2C%20across%20civilian%20infrastructure%2C%20that%20low%20blows%20aren't%20just%20a%20possibility%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Wray%20said.%20%26quot%3BLow%20blows%20against%20civilians%20are%20part%20of%20China's%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Wray%20has%20sounded%20the%20alarm%20on%20China's%20hacking%20prowess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Wray%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fchina-stealing-technology-secrets-five-eyes-intelligence-leaders-warn-60-minutes-transcript%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E60%20Minutes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20China%20has%20stolen%20more%20US%20data%20%26quot%3Bthan%20every%20nation%2C%20big%20or%20small%2C%20combined.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20as%20we%20sit%20here%20while%20important%20budget%20discussions%20are%20underway%2C%20I'll%20note%20that%20this%20is%20a%20time%20to%20be%20keeping%20ahead%20of%20the%20threat%20by%20investing%20in%20our%20capabilities%20rather%20than%20cutting%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Wray%20told%20lawmakers%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWray's%20assessment%20of%20China%20echoes%20that%20of%20his%20CIA%20counterpart%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcia-chief-ukraine-war-failure-for-russia-on-many-levels-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWilliam%20J.%20Burns%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Funited-states%2Fcia-spycraft-and-statecraft-william-burns%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForeign%20Affairs%20%3C%2Fa%3Eop-ed%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20CIA%20chief%20said%20that%20his%20agency%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcia-doubled-budget-china-greater-threat-russia-cia-chief-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20