F2024%2F01%2F31123528%2Ffig-4-20231219_101120-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31123528%2Ffig-4-20231219_101120-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695047%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERajkot%2C%20Malvan%2C%20December%2019%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Shukla%20Sawant%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31123726%2Ffig-5-20231219_113409.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31123726%2Ffig-5-20231219_113409.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31123726%2Ffig-5-20231219_113409-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31123726%2Ffig-5-20231219_113409-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20view%20of%20Rajkot%20from%20the%20Malvan%20pier%2C%20December%2019%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Shukla%20Sawant%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crowds%20visiting%20the%20site%20that%20morning%20comprised%20mainly%20of%20school%20students%20and%20the%20throng%2C%20on%20being%20disgorged%20from%20the%20buses%2C%20rent%20the%20air%20with%20battle%20cries%20as%20they%20made%20their%20way%20into%20the%20complex%20where%20the%20statue%20stands%20atop%20a%20high%20pedestal%2C%20facing%20outwards%20towards%20the%20Arabian%20Sea.%20This%20aural%20articulation%20of%20a%20combative%20nationalism%20by%20a%20group%20of%20youngsters%20was%20the%20main%20reason%20why%20the%20seagulls%20had%20taken%20flight%20to%20perch%20in%20safety%20on%20the%20highest%20point%20that%20they%20could%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sword%20wielding%20image%20of%20the%20Maratha%20king%20is%20a%20standardised%20template%20that%20appears%20in%20many%20different%20visual%20restatements%20across%20India%2C%20particularly%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20this%20statue%20made%20by%20a%20Sir%20Jamsetjee%20Jeejeebhoy%20School%20of%20Art%20alumnim%20Jaideep%20Apte%2C%20was%20no%20different.%20Grounded%20in%20European%20academic%20realism%20taught%20at%20the%20school%20since%20the%20mid%2019th%20century%2C%20where%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20learning%20the%20formal%20conventions%20of%20colonial%20representational%20forms%2C%20the%20grammar%20of%20academic%20body%20types%20was%20so%20internalised%20by%20the%20sculptor%20that%20he%20needed%20no%20visual%20model%20for%20his%20figurative%20interpretation.%20Through%20an%20interview%20given%20to%20me%2C%20I%20however%20learnt%20that%20the%20sculptor%20had%20given%20much%20thought%20to%20the%20figure%E2%80%99s%20directional%20symbolism.%20Facing%20north-west%2C%20the%20statue%20was%20aligned%20with%20great%20care%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20sword%20wielding%20warrior%20king%E2%80%99s%20sword-tip%20pointed%20outwards%20and%20away%20from%20the%20landmass%20of%20India%20and%20towards%20where%20sea-borne%20armies%20of%20potential%20colonisers%20would%20arrive%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20also%20a%20port%20city%20across%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20where%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20had%20carried%20out%20its%20%E2%80%98Operation%20Trident%E2%80%99%20on%20December%204-5%2C%201971%2C%20a%20date%20that%20eventually%20came%20to%20be%20designated%20as%20Indian%20Navy%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20projects%2C%20implemented%20in%20great%20haste%20to%20impact%20public%20memory%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election%20year%2C%20the%20process%20of%20making%20the%20sculpture%20was%20accelerated%20through%20the%20use%20of%20laser%20cutting%20machines%20and%203D%20printers%20provided%20literally%20overnight%20by%20a%20firm%20called%20Dream2reality%2C%20to%20print%20out%20the%20enlarged%20scan%20in%20pieces%20and%20sand%20cast%20it%20in%20two%20facilities%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20metropolitan%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20310px)%2085vw%2C%20310px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31124341%2Ffig-6.-IMG-20240102-WA0031.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22310%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31124341%2Ffig-6.-IMG-20240102-WA0031.jpg%20675w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31124341%2Ffig-6.-IMG-20240102-WA0031-169x300.jpg%20169w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31124341%2Ffig-6.-IMG-20240102-WA0031-576x1024.jpg%20576w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695049%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22551%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E3D%20printing%20of%20the%20Chattrapati%20Shivaji%20Statue%20by%20the%20Dream2reality%20team.%20Photo%3A%20Jaideep%20Apte%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31124424%2Ffig-7.-IMG-20240102-WA0026.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31124424%2Ffig-7.-IMG-20240102-WA0026.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31124424%2Ffig-7.-IMG-20240102-WA0026-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31124424%2Ffig-7.-IMG-20240102-WA0026-1024x1024.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31124424%2Ffig-7.-IMG-20240102-WA0026-150x150.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695050%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EInstalling%20the%20statue%20at%20Rajkot%2C%20Malvan%2C%20November%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Jaideep%20Apte%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20however%20unprecedented%20was%20that%20the%20commissioning%2C%20fabrication%20and%20installation%20of%20this%20monument%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaharashtratimes.com%2Fmaharashtra%2Fsindhudurg%2Fkalyan-sculpture-jaydeep-apte-sculpts-chhatrapati-shivaji-maharaj-statue-unveiled-by-pm-narendra-modi-in-sindhudurg-malvan-rajkot-fort%2Farticleshow%2F105769632.cms%5C%22%3Ecarried%20out%20with%20deep%20involvement%20of%20Naval%20officers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20an%20uncanny%20understanding%20of%20the%20political%20alignments%20of%20aesthetics%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20expansive%20knowledge%20of%20implementing%20a%20project%20with%20military%20precision.%20Once%20cast%2C%20the%20sculpture%20was%20transported%20in%20a%20truck%20and%20assembled%20on%20site%20just%20a%20few%20days%20before%20its%20consecration%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20for%20security%20reasons%20apparently%2C%20local%20skilled%20workers%20had%20a%20minimal%20role%20to%20play%20in%20scouting%20the%20site%2C%20with%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20the%20work%20being%20outsourced%20to%20men%20in%20uniform%20from%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Dockyards%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20Naval%20ships%20are%20repaired%20and%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacts%20and%20fiction%20have%20often%20been%20mingled%20in%20contemporary%20interpretations%20of%20the%20life%20and%20times%20of%20the%20Maratha%20king%2C%20which%20have%20been%20delved%20into%20by%20several%20writers%20in%20the%20past.%20However%2C%20my%20interest%20lies%20in%20something%20else%2C%20rather%20than%20another%20exploration%20of%20his%20historical%20legacy.%20What%20needs%20to%20be%20analysed%20is%20how%20a%20granular%20public%20memory%20is%20being%20pulverised%20and%20reconstituted%20through%20a%20vast%20digital%20operating%20system%2C%20to%20consolidate%20the%20visual%20field%20into%20a%20monocultural%20world%20view.%20Enough%20studies%20have%20been%20done%20on%20how%20political%20systems%20mobilise%20mass%20adulation%20through%20monumental%20statuary%20and%20marking%20of%20physical%20sites.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20era%20of%20social%20media%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20be%20attentive%20to%20how%20memory%20is%20being%20modified%20through%20the%20technical%20dominance%20of%20official%20image%20dispersion%20methodologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommunity%20memories%20of%20the%20Malvan%20event%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20have%20coalesced%20around%20the%20spectacular%20images%20put%20out%20by%20the%20government%20propaganda%20machinery%2C%20shot%20with%20high-end%20equipment%20of%20official%20photographers%20on%20duty%20and%20taken%20from%20unmatched%20viewing%20angles%20that%20only%20they%20had%20access%20to.%20My%20quest%20for%20images%20of%20the%20Navy%20Day%20%E2%80%98Operational%20Demonstration%E2%80%99%20taken%20by%20local%20residents%20a%20fortnight%20after%20the%20event%20yielded%20no%20results%20for%20quite%20some%20time.%20I%20was%20repeatedly%20directed%20to%20online%20repositories%20of%20official%20photographers%20by%20people%20who%20had%20nonetheless%20personally%20witnessed%20the%20events%2C%20even%20if%20from%20afar.%20Neither%20the%20local%20newspaper%20and%20not%20even%20the%20Malvan%20BJP%20office%20could%20give%20me%20access%20to%20photographs%20taken%20by%20their%20associates%2C%20even%20though%20they%20were%20listed%20as%20key%20organisers%20of%20the%20event%20in%20news%20stories%20that%20came%20out%20locally.%20A%20visit%20to%20three%20photo%20studios%20in%20town%2C%20who%20run%20a%20thriving%20business%20of%20wedding%20photography%20and%20passport%20photographs%2C%20also%20turned%20up%20a%20blank.%20On%20probing%20further%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20people%20who%20did%20take%20photographs%20had%2C%20not%20surprisingly%2C%20deleted%20them%20from%20their%20phones.%20For%20mobile%20phone%20photographs%20take%20up%20too%20much%20digital%20memory%20space%20and%20for%20many%2C%20they%20seem%20to%20be%20nothing%20more%20than%20an%20elongated%20pause%20of%20a%20fleeting%20moment%2C%20unless%20photography%20is%20their%20professional%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20sculpture%20was%20unveiled%20last%20December%2C%20the%20entire%20space%20around%20the%20site%20and%20staged%20ceremonies%20had%20been%C2%A0%20cordoned%20off%2C%20with%20views%20of%20what%20transpired%20made%20available%20for%20all%20only%20via%20officially%20mandated%20news%20outlets.%20The%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20now%20the%20most%20subscribed%20in%20the%20world%20of%20any%20political%20leader%2C%20has%20been%20very%20active%20since%20then%20in%20disseminating%20information%20about%20the%20event%20and%20his%20performative%20politics.%20No%20political%20leader%20in%20contemporary%20times%20has%20a%20better%20grasp%20of%20how%20ceremonial%20protocols%2C%20invented%20and%20performed%20for%20image%20enhancement%20and%20amplified%20via%20social%20media%2C%20work.%20The%20rituals%20are%20carefully%20choreographed%20for%20aura%20building%2C%20where%20distancing%20and%20staged%20proximity%20with%20the%20members%20of%20the%20public%20are%20of%20equal%20importance%2C%20as%20is%20their%20dispersal%20through%20a%20tightly%20controlled%20media%20that%20play%20out%20snippets%20of%20these%20performances%2C%20a%20manifestation%20of%20the%C2%A0%20biopolitical%20state%20that%20India%20has%20become%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F-wBsBZGYTiE%3Fsi%3D4VsyjdDg_olAOpOS%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C