riginID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fopen-ai-makes-it-easier-to-access-custom-gpts-in-chatgpt%2Farticleshow%2F107302754.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20introduces%20a%20new%20feature%20for%20ChatGPT%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20easily%20interact%20with%20custom%20GPTs.%20Users%20can%20now%20bring%20GPTs%20into%20any%20conversation%20by%20typing%20'%40'%20and%20selecting%20the%20desired%20GPT%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20to%20open%20the%20GPT%20Store.%20Similar%20to%20Google's%20Bard%2C%20users%20can%20now%20access%20relevant%20GPTs%20with%20full%20context%20in%20ChatGPT.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fopen-ai-makes-it-easier-to-access-custom-gpts-in-chatgpt%2Farticleshow%2F107302754.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bombay%20High%20Court%20Passes%20Split%20Verdict%20On%20Petition%20Challenging%20Fact-Checking%20Unit%20Rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F28022009%2FBombay-high-court-lit-up-at-night.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bombay%20high%20court%20on%20Wednesday%20(January%2031)%20delivered%20a%20split%20verdict%20on%20the%20petition%20seeking%20to%20strike%20down%20rules%203(i)(II)(A)%20and%20(C)%20of%20the%20IT%20Amendment%20Rules%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20rules%20give%20the%20Union%20government%20powers%20to%20set%20up%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfact-checking%20unit%E2%80%9D%20(FCU)%20to%20assess%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20term%20posts%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20stand-up%20comedian%20and%20political%20satirist%20Kunal%20Kamra%2C%20the%20Association%20of%20Indian%20Magazines%2C%20the%20News%20Broadcasters%20and%20Digital%20Association%20and%20the%20Editors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Gautam%20Patel%20and%20Neela%20Gokhale%20presided%20over%20the%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Justice%20Patel%20passed%20an%20order%20favouring%20the%20petitioners%2C%20Justice%20Gokhale%20upheld%20the%20amendment%20made%20to%20the%20Rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20will%20now%20be%20referred%20to%20another%20judge%20and%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20FCU%20will%20not%20be%20notified%20for%20the%20coming%20ten%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20amended%20rules%2C%20once%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20FCU%20identifies%20content%20as%20fake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading%2C%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20would%20either%20have%20to%20take%20the%20content%20down%20content%20or%20add%20a%20disclaimer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Patel%2C%20in%20a%20148-page%20order%2C%20however%2C%20observed%20that%20the%20state%20classifying%20speech%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctrue%20or%20false%E2%80%9D%20and%20compelling%20its%20non-publication%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Cnothing%20but%20censorship%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Navroz%20Seervai%2C%20appearing%20for%20Kamra%2C%20had%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20remedies%20available%20to%20social%20media%20platform%20users%20in%20the%20event%20of%20their%20content%20being%20flagged%20as%20fake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeervai%20had%20also%20argued%20that%20the%20said%20IT%20rule%20violates%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20battery%20of%20seasoned%20lawyers%2C%20including%20senior%20advocates%20Darius%20Khambata%20and%20Arvind%20Datar%20and%20advocates%20Shadan%20Farasat%20and%20Gautam%20Bhatia%2C%20appeared%20for%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20had%20pointed%20out%20that%20allowing%20the%20government%20to%20decide%20what%20is%20fake%20and%20false%20risks%20arbitrary%20and%20discriminative%20orders%20and%20would%20directly%20violate%20Articles%2014%20and%2019%20(1)(A)%20of%20the%20constitution%20along%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20natural%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDatar%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20rule%20attempts%20to%20exceed%20the%20restrictions%20imposed%20on%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20under%20Article%2019(2)%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2019(2)%20permits%20the%20government%20to%20impose%20%E2%80%9Creasonable%20restrictions%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20interests%20of%20public%20order%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20had%20spoken%20of%20the%20dangers%20of%20allowing%20fake%20news%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Justice%20Patel%20observed%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6in%20our%20constitutional%20scheme%2C%20free%20speech%20is%20always%20to%20be%20under-regulated%2C%20and%20the%20restrictions%20on%20it%20%E2%80%93%20attempts%20at%20control%20and%20abridgement%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20over-regulated%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20a%20finding%20that%20there%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right%20to%20falsehood%20or%20fake%20news%20or%20deepfakes.%20Quite%20the%20contrary.%20That%20is%20not%20even%20the%20question%20before%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20issue%20is%20whether%20the%20state%20has%2C%20in%20our%20constitutional%20set-up%2C%20an%20overriding%20authority%20to%20arrive%20at%20an%20absolutist%20determination%20of%20both%20content%20and%20expression%20as%20%E2%80%98the%20truth%E2%80%99%20and%20to%20compel%20a%20particular%20form%20of%20content%20and%20expression%3F%20I%20would%20have%20the%20greatest%20difficulty%20in%20accepting%20a%20proposition%20of%20this%20width.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20support%20his%20argument%2C%20Mehta%20had%20played%20video%20clips%20showing%20deepfakes%20of%20Hollywood%20actor%20Morgan%20Freeman%20and%20other%20well-known%20personalities%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gokhale%2C%20in%20her%2092-page%20order%20upholding%20the%20amended%20FCU%20clause%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20can%20belief%20in%20misinformation%20lead%20to%20poor%20judgments%20and%20decision%20making%2C%20but%20it%20also%20exerts%20a%20lingering%20influence%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20reasoning%20even%20after%20it%20has%20been%20corrected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20observed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdangers%20of%20fake%20news%20on%20social%20media%20intermediaries%20cannot%20be%20played%20down%20any%20longer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20in%20this%20scenario%20that%20the%20government%20appears%20to%20have%20framed%20the%20impugned%20rule%20to%20curb%20the%20menace%20of%20fake%2C%20false%2C%20and%20misleading%20information%20related%20to%20business%20of%20the%20government.%20On%20an%20exacting%20understanding%20of%20the%20rule%2C%20the%20information%20to%20be%20offensive%20must%20be%20shared%20with%20the%20knowledge%20that%20it%20is%20not%20genuine%20and%20is%20shared%20with%20malicious%20intent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20order%2C%20Justice%20Gokhale%20acknowledged%20that%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvibrant%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Clargest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%2C%20there%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Csuspicion%E2%80%9D%20regarding%20the%20intent%20of%20the%20government%20in%20introducing%20a%20provision%20such%20as%20the%20FCU%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20apprehensions%20of%20the%20petitioners%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Care%20also%20justified%20and%20cannot%20be%20swept%20away%20as%20frivolous%20or%20motivated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20regulating%20free%20speech%20to%20the%20limited%20extent%20of%20fake%2C%20false%20and%20misleading%20information%20in%20a%20way%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20create%20better%20conditions%20for%20citizens%20to%20sift%20facts%20from%20fake%20and%20make%20informed%20decisions%20about%20what%20and%20how%20they%20want%20their%20societies%20to%20be%2C%20based%20on%20an%20opportunity%20to%20receive%20unadulterated%20information.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Justice%20Gokhale%2C%20the%20rule%20%E2%80%9Cmeets%20the%20test%20of%20proportionality%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5D%20right%20of%20citizens%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20representative%20and%20participative%20democracy%20of%20the%20county%20is%20meaningless%20unless%20they%20have%20access%20to%20authentic%20information%20and%20are%20not%20misled%20by%20misinformation%2C%20information%20which%20is%20patently%20untrue%2C%20fake%2C%20false%2C%20or%20misleading%2C%20knowingly%20communicated%20with%20malicious%20intent%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%20in%20her%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGokhale%20also%20said%20that%20the%20measures%20adopted%20by%20the%20government%20are%20%E2%80%9Cconsistent%20with%20the%20object%20of%20the%20law%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20encroachment%20on%20a%20fundamental%20right%20is%20not%20disproportionate%20to%20the%20benefit%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20ensue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%2C%20however%2C%20observed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20unthinkable%20that%20any%20one%20entity%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20the%20government%20or%20anyone%20else%20%E2%80%93%20can%20unilaterally%20%E2%80%98identified%E2%80%99%2C%20(meaning%20picked%20out%20and%20decided)%20to%20be%20fake%2C%20false%20or%20misleading.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20surely%20cannot%20be%20the%20sole%20preserve%20of%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20observed%20as%20he%20went%20on%20to%20express%20his%20regret%20for%20not%20being%20able%20to%20persuade%20Justice%20Gokhale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20regret%20that%20I%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20persuade%20Justice%20Gokhale%20to%20my%20perspective%2C%20nor%20I%20to%20share%20hers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20concluding%20remark%20in%20the%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706726384000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F28022009%2FBombay-high-court-lit-up-at-night.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbombay-hc-split-verdict-petition-it-amendment-rules%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20matter%20will%20now%20be%20referred%20to%20another%20judge%20and%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20government's%20fact-checking%20unit%20will%20not%20be%20notified%20for%20the%20next%20ten%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbombay-hc-split-verdict-petition-it-amendment-rules%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Woman%20Arrested%20In%20Connection%20With%20Death%20Of%204-Year-Old%20Daughter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20in%20California%20was%20arrested%20after%20her%204-year-old%20daughter%20was%20found%20strangled%20to%20death%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabc7.com%2F4-year-old-girl-killed-mia-gonzalez-mother-arrested-east-los-angeles%2F14370528%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EABC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3ENews%20reported.%20The%20media%20outlet%20reported%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20murder%20after%20the%20young%20girl%20was%20found%20unresponsive%20in%20a%20car%20in%20East%20Los%20Angeles%20on%20Thursday%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20Sheriff's%20Department%20said%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20identified%20as%20Maria%20Avalos%2C%2038.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20woman%20has%20been%20charged%20officially%20but%20as%20per%20jail%20records%2C%20she%20is%20currently%20in%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%204-year-old%20was%20identified%20as%20Mia%20Gonzalez.%20%26quot%3BMia%20was%20a%20really%20good%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20godmother%20Noemi%20Lopez%20told%20KABC.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20the%20light%20of%20my%20home.%20She%20didn't%20deserve%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20found%20Mia%20in%20an%20unresponsive%20state%20following%20a%20report%20of%20a%20child%20assault%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20citing%20the%20police.%20She%20was%20declared%20dead%20at%20the%20hospital.%20The%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20Medical%20Examiner%20classifies%20Mia's%20cause%20of%20death%20as%20a%20homicide%2C%20resulting%20from%20both%20strangulation%20and%20a%20sharp%20force%20injury%20to%20the%20wrist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20told%20KABC%20that%20the%20investigators%20said%20Avalos%20could%20have%20been%20driving%20around%20with%20Mia's%20body%20for%20days%20before%20she%20was%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMia's%20family%20started%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fxgsvwm-mia-gonzalez%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGoFundMe%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20funeral%20expenses%2C%20which%20has%20raised%20over%20%241%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20pain%20in%20our%20hearts%20we%20are%20asking%20for%20help%20with%20the%20death%20of%20our%20little%20Mia%20Gonzalez%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20organizer%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BHer%20dad%20Jose%20Gonzalez%20along%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Gonzalez%20family%20and%20her%20godmother%20Noemi%20Lopez%20thank%20you%20for%20any%20donation%20for%20her%20funeral.%20God%20bless%20you%20and%20multiply%20your%20generosity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706725080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F6835sp0g_us-police-generic_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-woman-arrested-in-connection-with-death-of-4-year-old-daughter-4969466%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Los%20Angeles%20County%20Sheriff's%20Department%20said%20that%20the%20woman%20was%20identified%20as%20Maria%20Avalos%2C%2038.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-woman-arrested-in-connection-with-death-of-4-year-old-daughter-4969466%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-woman-arrested-in-connection-with-death-of-4-year-old-daughter-4969466%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fus-woman-arrested-in-connection-with-death-of-4-year-old-daughter-4969466%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20Maoists%20In%20Chhattisgarh%20Are%20Targeting%20New%20'Tatkal%20Camps'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAnti-Maoist%20operations%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20have%20entered%20a%20new%20phase%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20in%20December%20last%20year.%20Security%20forces%20have%20set%20up%20Tatkal%20Camps%20(Instant%20Camps)%20in%20the%20areas%20which%20are%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20den%20of%20Maoists.%20Almost%20a%20dozen%20camps%20have%20been%20set%20up%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20December%20which%20has%20left%20the%20Maoists%20baffled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20camps%20have%20come%20up%20in%20regions%20that%20are%20badly%20affected%20by%20Maoist%20attacks.%20Padia%2C%20Muler%2C%20Salatong%20in%20the%20Sukma%20district%2C%20Murkarajbeda%2C%20Duled%2C%20Dumripalnar%2C%20Palnar%20and%20Mutavendi%20are%20some%20regions%20where%20these%20camps%20have%20been%20set%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttacks%20On%20Tatkal%20Camps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20camps%20are%20becoming%20new%20targets.%20Three%20security%20personnel%20were%20killed%20and%2014%20others%20were%20injured%20in%20a%20gunfight%20with%20Maoists%20near%20the%20Bijapur-Sukma%20border%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20yesterday%20when%20they%20were%20working%20to%20establish%20the%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20camp%20was%20established%20in%20Tekulagudem%20village%20in%20the%20Sukma%20district%20to%20provide%20the%20people%20of%20the%20area%20with%20basic%20facilities%20and%20keep%20a%20check%20on%20Maoist%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOperations%20are%20being%20conducted%20daily%20due%20to%20which%20the%20force%20is%20on%20the%20move%20always.%20Tatkal%20camps%20are%20being%20set%20up%20and%20sometimes%20security%20parameters%20are%20overlooked%20due%20to%20which%20such%20attacks%20are%20taking%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20on%20the%20ground%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20attack%20on%20Tekelgudem%20village%20on%20the%20Sukma-Bijapur%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20camp%20was%20being%20set%20up%20in%20Tekelgudem%2C%20the%20forces%20were%20trying%20to%20secure%20the%20adjoining%20area%20and%20one%20party%20was%20attacked%20by%20Maoists%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20told%20NDTV.%20This%20is%20the%20second%20attack%20in%20this%20region%2C%20the%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20in%20April%2C%20when%20security%20forces%20entered%20the%20region%2C%2023%20soldiers%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20locals%20are%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20camps.%20In%20the%20Silgir%20village%2C%20several%20villagers%20are%20protesting%20against%20the%20Tatkal%20Camps.%20The%20protest%20is%20taking%20place%20a%20few%20kilometres%20from%20where%20the%20attack%20took%20place.%20In%20Bastar%2C%2023%20protests%20are%20taking%20place%20against%20the%20establishment%20of%20these%20security%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20Forces%20Putting%20Special%20Focus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20on%20the%20ground%20said%20Tekelgudem%20in%20the%20state%20has%20been%20infested%20with%20Maoists%20for%20the%20last%20four%20decades%2C%20because%20of%20which%20development%20is%20not%20taking%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20told%20NDTV%20that%20%26quot%3BFormer%20Maoist%20commander%20Hidma%20lives%20four%20kilometres%20from%20here%20and%20therefore%20nearby%20villages%20including%20Tekelgudem%20do%20not%20have%20roads%2C%20electricity%2C%20school%20and%20hospitals.%20Maoists%20are%20forcing%20villagers%20to%20join%20their%20organizations.%20Children%20in%20the%20region%20are%20taught%20about%20Maoism%20to%20recruit%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20reiterated%20that%20the%20menace%20would%20be%20over%20in%20India%20in%20the%20next%20three%20years.%20Security%20forces%20have%20been%20planning%20operations%20on%20the%20ground%20meticulously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20on%20January%2016%2C%20more%20than%20400%20Maoists%20attacked%20the%20Dharmavaram%20camp%20and%20tried%20to%20divert%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20security%20forces%20by%20firing%20more%20than%20a%20thousand%20barrel%20grenade%20launchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20forces%20have%20put%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20Dandakaranya%20its%20neighbouring%20regions.%20Dandakaranya%20Special%20Zonal%20Committee%20(DKSZC)%20of%20the%20central%20regional%20bureau%20of%20the%20CPI(Maoist)%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20Maoist%20stronghold%20and%20shelter%20zone%20of%20the%20brass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20central%20committee%20members%20are%20stationed%20in%20the%20Dandakaranya%20zone%2C%20which%20has%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20functionally%20compact%20zone%20administratively%20for%20the%20Maoists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20area%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20the%20government%20as%20the%20last%20stronghold%20of%20the%20Maoists%20after%20facing%20losses%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706724600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fm68ijrqs_crpf-generic-maoist-encounter-ani_625x300_12_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-maoists-in-chhattisgarh-are-targeting-new-tatkal-camps-4969429%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anti-Maoist%20operations%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20have%20entered%20a%20new%20phase%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20in%20December%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-maoists-in-chhattisgarh-are-targeting-new-tatkal-camps-4969429%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-maoists-in-chhattisgarh-are-targeting-new-tatkal-camps-4969429%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-maoists-in-chhattisgarh-are-targeting-new-tatkal-camps-4969429%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hemant%20Soren%20Arrested%2C%20Champai%20Soren%20To%20Take%20Over%20As%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20this%20evening%2C%20minutes%20after%20quitting%20the%20post.%20Transport%20minister%20Champai%20Soren%2C%20one%20of%20the%20veteran%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%2C%20will%20step%20into%20his%20shoes.%20Later%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20was%20formally%20arrested%20after%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20ED%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHemant%20Soren%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam%2C%20minutes%20after%20meeting%20the%20governor%20and%20handing%20in%20his%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20he%20had%20discussed%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20officials%2C%20declaring%20that%20he%20would%20sign%20the%20arrest%20memo%20only%20after%20stepping%20down.%20The%20ED%20Officials%20then%20took%20him%20to%20meet%20the%20Governor.%20A%20Chief%20Minister%20can%20be%20arrested%20under%20the%20anti-money%20laundering%20rules%20if%20he%20evades%20summons%20thrice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%2C%20after%20evading%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20over%20the%20weekend%2C%20had%20agreed%20to%20be%20questioned%20by%20the%20Central%20agency%20this%20afternoon.%20His%20statement%20was%20recorded%20during%20the%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20posted%20some%20Hindi%20verses%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%20Their%20rough%20translation%20read%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bit's%20a%20break%3Cbr%3E%5Cnlife%20is%20a%20great%20battle%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20have%20fought%20every%20moment%2C%20I%20will%20fight%20every%20moment%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20I%20will%20not%20beg%20for%20compromise%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20in%20defeat%2C%20what%20in%20victory%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20am%20not%20afraid%20at%20all%3Cbr%3E%5Cnsmallness%20don't%20touch%20me%20now%3Cbr%3E%5Cnyou%20are%20great%2C%20keep%20it%20up%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethe%20pain%20of%20the%20hearts%20of%20our%20people%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20will%20not%20give%20up%20in%20vain%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20will%20not%20accept%20defeat...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20Jharkhand!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20had%20evaded%20seven%20summons%20for%20questioning%20in%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Rs%20600%20crore%20land%20scam%2C%20was%20anticipating%20arrest%20for%20a%20while.%C2%A0%20Yesterday%2C%20he%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20MLAs%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20where%20the%20question%20of%20his%20successor%20was%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20it%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20his%20wife%2C%20Kalpana%20Soren.%20But%20given%20the%20proximity%20of%20the%20state%20elections%20--%20due%20in%20November%20--%20the%20party%20had%20to%20drop%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy-elections%20cannot%20be%20held%20in%20the%20last%20year%20of%20any%20state%20assembly's%20term%20and%20so%2C%20Kalpana%20Soren%20could%20not%20have%20been%20elected%20an%20MLA%20even%20if%20she%20was%20named%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20scam%20involves%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20racket%26quot%3B%20to%20change%20of%20ownership%20of%20government%20land%20and%20selling%20it%20to%20builders%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20alleged.%20So%20far%2C%2014%20people%20have%20been%C2%A0%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%2C%20including%202011-batch%20IAS%20officer%20Chhavi%20Ranjan%20who%20served%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20state%20Social%20Welfare%20Department%20and%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Ranchi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20has%20claimed%20that%20he%20is%20the%20target%20of%20a%20huge%20conspiracy.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20conspiracy%20against%20him%20has%20succeeded%20for%20a%20while.%20But%20our%20government%20has%20majority%20and%20will%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20state%20minster%20Mithilesh%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706723940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fuobh5lkg_hemant-soren-pti_625x300_04_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-to-quit-minister-champai-soren-to-meet-governor-to-take-over-4968368%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20this%20evening%2C%20minutes%20after%20quitting%20the%20post.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-to-quit-minister-champai-soren-to-meet-governor-to-take-over-4968368%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-to-quit-minister-champai-soren-to-meet-governor-to-take-over-4968368%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-to-quit-minister-champai-soren-to-meet-governor-to-take-over-4968368%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thai%20W