's%20officials%20had%20not%20found%20the%20JMM%20leader%20there%20-%20leading%20to%20jibes%20from%20the%20BJP%20of%20him%20being%20'on%20the%20run'%20-%20they%20had%20seized%20Rs%2036%20lakh%20in%20cash%20and%20a%20BMW%20car%20which%2C%20they%20claimed%2C%20belonged%20to%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20had%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20senior%20officers%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20Ranchi%20office%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20in%20connection%20with%20Monday's%20operation.%20In%20his%20complaint%2C%20the%20JMM%20leader%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20a%20scheduled%20tribe%2C%20claimed%20the%20action%20harassed%20and%20maligned%20him%20and%20his%20entire%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20BMW%20or%20the%20cash%20that%20was%20seized%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20that%20the%20agency's%20officers%20had%20leaked%20%26quot%3Bselective%20misinformation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706720880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F01jqu538_hemant-soren-_625x300_31_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-resigns-hemant-soren-arrest-hemant-soren-refused-to-sign-arrest-memo-until-he-resigned-sources-4968717%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Top%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officials%20told%20NDTV%20that%20Mr%20Soren%20refused%20to%20sign%20his%20arrest%20memo%20until%20he%20submitted%20his%20resignation%20to%20Jharkhand%20Governor%20CP%20Radhakrishnan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-resigns-hemant-soren-arrest-hemant-soren-refused-to-sign-arrest-memo-until-he-resigned-sources-4968717%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-r