chief%20minister%20were%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20handed%E2%80%9D%20and%20reeked%20of%20a%20political%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChempai%20Soren%20is%20considered%20close%20to%20Hemant%20Soren%20and%20is%20a%20legislator%20from%20the%20Saraikela%20constituency.%20He%20is%20hugely%20popular%20in%20his%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahua%20Maji%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20has%20confirmed%20to%20the%20media%20that%20Hemant%20Soren%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20although%20the%20ED%20is%20yet%20to%20give%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Ranchi%2C%20Jharkhand%3A%20JMM%20MP%20Mahua%20Maji%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20CM%20is%20in%20ED%20custody.%20The%20CM%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20Governor%20with%20the%20ED%20team%20to%20submit%20his%20resignation%E2%80%A6%20Champai%20Soren%20will%20be%20the%20new%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%A6%20We%20have%20enough%20numbers%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPbumz1cUg0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FPbumz1cUg0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1752712889444843907%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20coalition%20led%20by%20the%20JMM%20enjoys%20a%20majority%20of%2049%20legislators%20in%20the%2081-member%20assembly.%20All%20legislators%20are%20reportedly%20unanimous%20in%20choosing%20Chempai%20Soren%20to%20replace%20Hemant%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%2029%20from%20the%20JMM%2C%2016%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20one%20from%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%2C%20one%20from%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist-Leninist)%20Liberation%20(CPI(ML)L)%20and%20o