h's%20Return%20to%20NDA%3A%20It's%20Wrong%20to%20Conclude%20a%20Cakewalk%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bihar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28163221%2F400924413_926965212122173_7713585483950685171_n.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EHas%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20lost%20the%20battle%20in%20Bihar%20by%20taking%20away%20Nitish%20Kumar%20from%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%3F%20Would%20it%20become%20difficult%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20weaken%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20in%20Bihar%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%2C%20of%20course%2C%20has%20got%20psychological%20advantage%20by%20bringing%20the%20Bihar%20CM%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20president%20from%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20of%20which%20he%20was%20the%20architect.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20palpable%20anger%20among%20the%20people%20against%20Nitish.%20The%20BJP%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20accepting%20him%20back%20to%20its%20fold%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20election%20strategist%20turned%20activist%2C%20Prashant%20Kishor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishore%20predicted%2C%20%E2%80%9CIrrespective%20of%20whatever%20alliance%20Nitish%20contests%20with%2C%20his%20party%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20win%20more%20than%2020%20seats%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%E2%80%9D%20Kishore%2C%20who%20is%20on%20his%20Jan%20Suraj%20%3Cem%3Epadyatra%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20north%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Begusarai%20district%20these%20days%2C%20has%20been%20advancing%20this%20argument%20in%20his%20speeches%20as%20well%20as%20his%20interviews%20with%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20widely%20held%20%E2%80%98assumption%E2%80%99%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20victory%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdone%20deal%E2%80%9D%20particularly%20after%20Nitish%20jumping%20to%20its%20side%20has%20subsumed%20the%20likely%20troubles%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20might%20face%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20expected%20in%20April-May%2C%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20and%20foremost%20trouble%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20all%20set%20to%20face%20is%20over%20sharing%20of%20seats.%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20JDU%20and%20the%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(LJP)%20of%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20(alive%20then)%20were%20the%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%20led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%202019.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20JDU%20had%20shared%2017%20seats%20each%2C%20sparing%20six%20seats%20for%20the%20LJP.%20The%20NDA%20had%20won%2039%20seats%E2%80%94BJP-17%2C%20JDU-16%20and%20LJP-6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20besides%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20JDU%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20Upendra%20Kushwaha%E2%80%99s%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Samata%20Party%20(RLSP)%2C%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%E2%80%99s%20Hindustani%20Aawam%20Morcha%20%E2%80%93%20Secular%20(HAMS)%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%E2%80%99s%20LJP%20and%20his%20uncle%20Pashupatinath%20Paras%E2%80%99s%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(RLJP)%20are%20in%20the%20NDA.%20Creating%20a%20buzz%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Ram%20temple%20and%20around%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98persona%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20BJP%20cadres%20are%20clamouring%20for%20more%20seats%20than%20what%20they%20had%20contested%20in%20Bihar%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RLSP%2C%20the%20HAMS%2C%20the%20LJP%20and%20the%20RLJP%2C%20which%20have%20been%20with%20the%20BJP%20from%20before%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20JDU%20has%20joined%20it%2C%20are%2C%20obviously%2C%20expecting%20their%20share%20of%20seats.%20There%20are%20only%2040%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20to%20share%20with.%20How%20many%20seats%20the%20BJP%20will%20keep%20in%20its%20share%20and%20how%20much%20will%20it%20spare%20for%20its%20five%20other%20partners%3F%20Needless%20to%20say%20that%20there%20is%20an%20apparent%20disquiet%20in%20the%20camps%20of%20these%20parties%20on%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20return%20in%20the%20NDA%3B%20their%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20was%20obvious%20at%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20ninth%20swearing-in%20as%20the%20CM%20at%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Raj%20Bhavan%20on%20Saturday-January%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98hullabaloo%E2%80%99%20of%20how%20the%20BJP%20has%20%E2%80%98dismantled%E2%80%99%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20by%20taking%20away%20Nitish%20from%20it%20and%20how%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20locked%20in%20crisis%20over%20seat%20sharing%20in%20Bengal%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20media%20is%20largely%20ignoring%20the%20challenges%20the%20BJP%20might%20face%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3EGround%20reality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatistics%20suggest%20that%20though%20Nitish%20has%20managed%20to%20retain%20his%20position%20as%20the%20CM%20despite%20his%20five%20flip-flops%2C%20he%20has%20increasingly%20lost%20his%20popularity%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%20His%20JDU%20had%20bagged%20barely%20two%20seats%20in%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20at%20the%20time%20when%20the%20CM%20had%20broken%20out%20with%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20suffered%20a%20dent%20in%20his%20image.%20His%20JDU%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20contested%20the%202015%20assembly%20polls%20in%20alliance%2C%20sharing%20101%20seats%20each%20between%20them.%20The%20JDU%20bagged%2071%20seats%20against%20the%20RJD%E2%80%99s%2080.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU%20contested%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20which%20the%20JDU%20got%20122%20seats%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20121%20in%20its%20share.%20But%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%2076%20seats%20against%20the%20JDU%E2%80%99s%2043%20(45%20now%20by%20splitting%20the%20LJP).%20The%20JDU%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20by%20propping%20Chirag%20Paswan%20to%20contest%20against%20the%20JDU%20candidates%20had%20caused%20its%20defeat%20in%2032%20seats.%20But%20the%20fact%20remains%20that%20the%20voters%20voted%20against%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20party.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20RJD%20led%20by%20Tejaswhi%20Yadav%20almost%20retained%20its%20tally%20(79)%2C%20emerging%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20despite%20the%20JDU%20had%20gone%20back%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Thus%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20elections%20from%202014%20onwards%20clearly%20suggest%20substantial%20loss%20of%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20clout%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20BJP%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20bringing%20Nitish%20back%20to%20its%20fold%E2%80%9D%20sounds%20convincing%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20statistics%20related%20to%20the%20elections%20from%202014%20onwards.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20will%20be%20well%20nigh%20impossible%20for%20Nitish%20to%20claim%20the%20credit%20for%20the%20caste%20survey%2C%20increasing%20the%20reservation%20up-to%2065%25%20and%20giving%20over%20four%20lakh%20jobs%20after%20dumping%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20and%20jumping%20back%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20reaction%20on%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20exit%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20on%20his%C2%A0%3Cem%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0at%20Purnia%20on%20Tuesday-January%2030%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Mahagathbandhan%20will%20fight%20for%20social%20justice%20in%20Bihar%3B%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20Nitish%20Kumar%20for%20that%20purpose%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20require%20him%20at%20all%E2%80%9D.%20The%20grand%20party%20scion%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20is%20quite%20logical%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20departure%20has%20made%20it%20relatively%20easy%20for%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20to%20share%20seats%20among%20its%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.01-PM-e1693560384596.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.01-PM-e1693560384596.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.01-PM-e1693560384596-300x114.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145236%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.01-PM-e1693560384596-1024x389.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671033%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22456%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ELeaders%20of%20parties%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20September%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RJD%20which%20is%20the%20largest%20partner%20in%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20has%20got%20more%20space%20to%20accommodate%20the%20claim%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left%20parties%20(CPI-ML-Liberation%2C%20CPI%20and%20CPM)%20which%20are%20inherently%20uncompromising%20with%20the%20Hindutva%20and%20designed%20to%20contest%20the%20elections%20for%20the%20larger%20cause%20of%20secularism%20and%20social%20and%20economic%20justice%20that%20involves%20the%20issues%20of%20price-rise%2C%20livelihood%2C%20health%2C%20disparity%2C%20deprivation%20and%20segregation%20of%20the%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%E2%80%94a%20smart%20operator%20of%20power%20game%20despite%20his%20old%20age%2C%20ailments%20and%20heat%20of%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20%E2%80%93%20might%20be%20looking%20for%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20Upendra%20Kushwaha%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20and%20others%20in%20case%20they%20were%20denied%20the%20desired%20share%20of%20seats%20and%20desert%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20RJD%20at%20its%20meeting%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Nitish%20exit%20from%20Mahagathbandhan%20has%20authorized%20Lalu%E2%80%94the%20RJD%20president%E2%80%94to%20take%20all%20the%20decisions%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20new%20developments%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20asserted%20that%20his%20party%20would%20win%20%E2%80%9C40%20out%20of%2040%20seats%E2%80%9D%20in%20Bihar%20with%20Nitish%20back%20in%20the%20NDA.%20But%20much%20water%20might%20flow%20down%20the%20Ganga%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706706035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28163221%2F400924413_926965212122173_7713585483950685171_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitishs-return-to-nda-its-wrong-to-conclude-a-cakewalk-for-the-bjp-in-bihar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20to%20do%20lot%20of%20explaining%20in%20the%20months%20to%20come%20by%20accepting%20Nitish%20Kumar%20into%20fold%20despite%20its%20fading%20popularity.%20He%20may%20well%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20liability%20than%20bringing%20anything%20to%20the%20BJP's%20kitty.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnitishs-return-to-nda-its-wrong-to-conclude-a-cakewalk-for-the-bjp-in-bihar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chinese%20hackers%20preparing%20to%20'wreak%20havoc'%20on%20US%2C%20warns%20FBI%20chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706705820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F768x432%2Fskynews-hacker-cyberattack_6439404.jpg%3F20240131153309%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fchinese-hackers-preparing-to-wreak-havoc-on-us-warns-fbi-chief-christopher-wray-13060726%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cyber%20hackers%20working%20for%20the%20Chinese%20government%20are%20preparing%20to%20%26quot%3Bwreak%20havoc%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20US%2C%20FBI%20director%20Christopher%20Wray%20is%20warning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fchinese-hackers-preparing-to-wreak-havoc-on-us-warns-fbi-chief-christopher-wray-13060726%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchinese-hackers-preparing-to-wreak-havoc-on-us-warns-fbi-chief-christopher-wray-13060726%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchinese-hackers-preparing-to-wreak-havoc-on-us-warns-fbi-chief-christopher-wray-13060726%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20Why%20the%20BJP%20Brings%20up%20the%20CAA%20%E2%80%93%20But%20Stops%20Short%20of%20Implementing%20it%20%E2%80%93%20in%20Bengal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31130931%2FGE8fscTaoAAgkEx.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20years%20after%20widespread%20protests%20across%20the%20country%20put%20the%20controversial%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20on%20the%20back%20burner%2C%20it%20is%20back%20on%20the%20political%20agenda%20before%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20and%20Union%20ministers%2C%20both%20from%20West%20Bengal%20%E2%80%93%20Shantanu%20Thakur%20and%20Nisith%20Pramanik%20%E2%80%93%20have%20publicly%20announced%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20plans%20to%20implement%20the%20CAA%20in%20the%20upcoming%20days.%20While%20Matua%20community%20leader%20Santanu%20Thakur%20gave%20%E2%80%9Ca%20week%E2%80%99s%E2%80%9D%20deadline%2C%20Pramanik%20who%20is%20a%20prominent%20presence%20in%20North%20Bengal%20refused%20to%20specify%20a%20timeline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20December%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20addressing%20a%20BJP%20rally%20in%20Kolkata%20asserted%20that%20the%20CAA%20is%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20and%20no%20force%20could%20prevent%20its%20implementation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20announcement%20is%20again%20expected%20to%20become%20a%20major%20issue%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20where%20BJP%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20consolidate%20lower%20caste%20Hindu%20votes%20by%20posturing%20itself%20as%20a%20protector%20of%20their%20interests.%20The%20party%20has%20been%20steadily%20making%20inroads%20into%20two%20of%20the%20largest%20Scheduled%20Caste%20segments%2C%20the%20Rajbanshi%20and%20Namashudra%20communities%20which%20constitute%2018.35%25%20and%2017.41%25%20of%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20total%20Scheduled%20Caste%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdoes-bjps-revival-of-the-caa-issue-reflect-the-partys-desperation-in-bengal%5C%22%3EDoes%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Revival%20of%20the%20CAA%20Issue%20Reflect%20the%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Desperation%20in%20Bengal%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERajbanshis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajbanshis%2C%20the%20largest%20SC%20group%20in%20the%20state%2C%20account%20for%20an%20estimated%2030%25%20of%20the%20North%20Bengal%20population.%20All%20five%20of%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20which%20have%20more%20than%2015%25%20of%20Rajbanshi%20population%20went%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20party%20also%20won%2030%20of%20the%2050%20assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20region%20in%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%2C%20but%20lost%20ground%20to%20TMC%20significantly%20in%20the%20last%20panchayat%20elections.%20The%20induction%20of%20Rajbanshi%20leader%20Ananta%20Maharaj%20into%20the%20BJP%20and%20his%20nomination%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20the%20party%20last%20year%20point%20to%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20community%20in%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20arithmetic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20Rajbashis%20are%20not%20enthusiastic%20about%20the%20CAA%2C%20says%C2%A0Ayan%20Guha%2C%20a%20political%20analyst%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Curious%20Trajectory%20of%20Caste%20in%20West%20Bengal%20Politics.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fi%3ERather%2C%20there%20is%20some%20degree%20of%20suspicion%20among%20the%20Rajbanshis%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20CAA.%20CAA%20will%20regularise%20the%20settlement%20of%20Bengali%20Hindu%20refugees%20whom%20the%20indigenous%20population%20of%20North%20Bengal%20%E2%80%93%20comprising%20communities%20like%C2%A0%20the%20Rajbanshis%20have%20traditionally%20regarded%20as%20outsiders%2C%E2%80%9D%20Guha%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPredictably%2C%20the%20announcement%20was%20met%20with%20severe%20criticism%20from%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20exploiting%20the%20citizenship%20law%20for%20electoral%20gains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20Rajbangshi%20friends%20have%20always%20been%20citizens.%20This%20sudden%20focus%20on%20CAA%20is%20nothing%20but%20election%20drama.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20already%20recognised%20them%2C%20granted%20them%20a%20permanent%20settlement%2C%20and%20included%20them%20in%20our%20welfare%20schemes.%20If%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20citizens%2C%20how%20could%20they%20have%20exercised%20their%20basic%20rights%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Banerjee%20while%20addressing%20a%20public%20event%20in%20Cooch%20Behar%20in%20North%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBorder%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECM%20Banerjee%20had%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20BSF%E2%80%99s%20discriminatory%20identity%20card%20policy%20for%20border%20residents%20and%20urged%20people%20to%20reject%20these%20documents%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctheir%20names%20would%20be%20deleted%20from%20the%20NRC%E2%80%9D%20should%20they%20do%20so.%20Around%2027%25%20voters%20of%20Cooch%20Behar%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20belong%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20for%20whom%20the%20NRC%20remains%20a%20burning%20issue.%20During%20the%202021%20assembly%20election%2C%20in%20the%20Sitalkuchi%20block%20of%20the%20district%2C%20CISF%20firing%20led%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20four%20villagers.%20The%20incident%20had%20a%20polarising%20impact%20across%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBoth%20BJP%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20for%20electoral%20gain.%20They%20want%20religious%20polarization%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20talking%20about%20NRC%20and%20CAA%20to%20create%20fear%20among%20citizens.%20No%20one%20can%20displace%20citizens%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20CPI(M)%20state%20secretary%20Mohammed%20Salim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAA%2C%20passed%20in%202019%2C%20offers%20a%20fast-track%20path%20to%20citizenship%20for%20non-Muslim%20religious%20minorities%20(Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20and%20Christians)%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%20who%20entered%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%20It%20sparked%20widespread%20protests%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20its%20discriminatory%20nature%20and%20potential%20connection%20to%20the%20NRC%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20identify%20and%20deport%20illegal%20immigrants.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Full%20Text%20%7C%20BJP's%20Exclusion%20of%20Muslims%20Is%20'Unacceptably%20Barbaric'%2C%20Says%20Amartya%20Sen%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Ffull-text-bjps-exclusion-of-muslims-is-unacceptably-barbaric-says-amartya-sen%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Exclusion%20of%20Muslims%20Is%20%E2%80%98Unacceptably%20Barbaric%E2%80%99%2C%20Says%20Amartya%20Sen%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CAA%20certainly%20lends%20itself%20to%20calculations%20concerning%20the%20impending%20general%20elections%20and%20it%20is%20here%20that%20the%20Matua%20community%20also%20comes%20in%2C%20feels%20the%20author%20Guha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20the%20Matuas%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20aspects%20of%20such%20calculations%20%E2%80%93%20one%20relates%20to%20the%20Namashudra%20Matua%20community%20and%20the%20other%20pertains%20to%20the%20pro-Hindu%20messaging%20to%20the%20population%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20pro-Hindu%20narrative%20encoded%20in%20the%20CAA%20is%20aimed%20at%20consolidating%20the%20traditional%20Hindu%20vote%20bank%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Guha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Matuas%20belong%20to%20the%20Namashudra%20caste%2C%20which%20stands%20outside%20the%20traditional%20four-tier%20Hindu%20caste%20system.%20Historically%20labeled%20as%20%E2%80%9CChandals%E2%80%9D%20and%20subjected%20to%20no%20end%20of%20derogatory%20terms%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Matuas%20organised%20a%20movement%20in%20the%20mid-19th%20century%20in%20Faridpur%20district%20of%20what%20is%20now%20Bangladesh.%20Icon%20Harichand%20Thakur%20led%20this%20caste%20uprising%2C%20establishing%20the%20Matua%20Mahasangha%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Vaishnavite%20Hindu%20sect%20that%20rejected%20the%20caste%20system.%20After%20Harichand%E2%80%99s%20death%20in%201878%2C%20his%20son%20Guruchand%20Thakur%20furthered%20the%20movement%E2%80%99s%20influence%2C%20attracting%20various%20Dalit%20groups.%20During%20the%20Partition%20of%20Bengal%2C%20many%20members%20of%20these%20social%20groups%20migrated%20from%20to%20West%20Bengal%2C%20significantly%20impacting%20the%20demographic%20landscape%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%20forming%20the%20second%20largest%20Scheduled%20Caste%20group%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20comprising%203.8%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20the%20Matuas%20have%20long%20been%20demanding%20proper%20rehabilitation%20and%20resettlement%20of%20Hindu%20Bengali%20refugees%20from%20Bangladesh.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20strategically%20initiated%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20poll%20campaign%20in%20the%20state%20from%20Thakurnagar%2C%20the%20Matua%20Mahasangha%20headquarters%2C%20expressing%20strong%20support%20for%20the%20CAA.%20BJP%20comprehensively%20won%20Ranaghat%20and%20Bangagon%2C%20two%20Matua-dominated%20seats%20in%20Nadia%20and%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20and%20narrowly%20lost%20Krishnanagar%20to%20TMC.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Orakandi%2C%20a%20sacred%20place%20for%20the%20Matuas%2C%20during%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly%20elections%20in%202021%2C%20further%20solidified%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20consolidation%20of%20the%20community.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Fwest-bengal-assembly%2Fcsds-lokniti-survey-finds-whether-subaltern-hindutva-is-on-the-wane%2Farticle34494129.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CSDS%20Lokniti%20Poll%20Poll%20survey%2C%2058%25%20of%20the%20Namashudra%20community%20voted%20for%20BJP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20helping%20them%20to%20secure%2014%20of%20the%2015%20seats%20in%20the%20Matua%20belt%20of%20Nadia%20and%20North%2024-Parganas.%20However%2C%20in%20the%202023%20panchayat%20polls%2C%20the%20Matua%20vote%20again%20shifted%20to%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20won%2049%20out%20of%20the%2053%20panchayats%20in%20these%20areas.%20The%20BJP%20won%20only%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20simple%20and%20necessary%20correlation%20between%20finalisation%20of%20the%20CAA%20rules%20and%20greater%20Matua%20support%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP.%20The%20framing%20of%20the%20CAA%20rules%20after%20an%20inordinate%20delay%20will%20definitely%20please%20the%20Matuas%20and%20naturally%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20try%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20finalisation%20of%20these%20rules.%20But%20in%20the%20longer%20run%2C%20the%20Matua%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20will%20depend%20upon%20how%20liberal%20and%20effective%20these%20rules%20are%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20citizenship%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Guha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20BJP%20needs%20to%20straddle%20the%20ambitions%20of%20two%20of%20the%20main%20communities%20in%20its%20Bengal%20support%20base%20with%20the%20CAA.%20While%20one%20favours%20the%20law%2C%20the%20other%20does%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706704236000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31130931%2FGE8fscTaoAAgkEx.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheres-why-the-bjp-brings-up-the-caa-but-stops-short-of-implementing-it-in-bengal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20and%20Union%20ministers%2C%20both%20from%20West%20Bengal%20%E2%80%93%20Shantanu%20Thakur%20and%20Nisith%20Pramanik%20%E2%80%93%20have%20publicly%20announced%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20plans%20to%20implement%20the%20CAA%20in%20the%20upcoming%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheres-why-the-bjp-brings-up-the-caa-but-stops-short-of-implementing-it-in-bengal%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hemant%20Soren%20Files%20Case%20Against%20Probe%20Agency%20Under%20SC%2FST%20Act%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20speculation%20about%20Hemant%20Soren's%20imminent%20arrest%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20has%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20senior%20officers%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20Ranchi%20office%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%20The%20complaint%2C%20filed%20at%20the%20SC%2FST%20police%20station%20in%20Ranchi%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20pertains%20to%20the%20agency's%20search%20operation%20at%20Mr%20Soren's%20residence%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20claims%20that%20the%20action%20harassed%20and%20maligned%20him%20and%20his%20entire%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20belongs%20to%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20lodged%20against%20some%20senior%20ED%20officials...%20we%20got%20the%20application%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%26quot%3B%20Ranchi%20Senior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Chandan%20Kumar%20Sinha%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20is%20being%20questioned%20by%20the%20ED%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Ranchi%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam.%20There%20is%20a%20strong%20buzz%20that%20he%20may%20be%20arrested%20and%20his%20party%20has%20reportedly%20also%20planned%20for%20that%20eventuality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency's%20operation%20at%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister's%20Delhi%20home%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-news-enforcement-directorate-hemant-sorens-big-road-trip-as-probe-agency-waited-at-delhi-home-private-plane-4965766%5C%22%3Ehad%20turned%20dramati%3C%2Fa%3Ec%20on%20Monday%20after%20ED%20officials%20reached%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20question%20him%2C%20but%20could%20not%20find%20him%20there.%20They%20seized%20Rs%2036%20lakh%20in%20cash%20and%20a%20BMW%20X7%2C%20which%20costs%20over%20Rs%201%20crore.%C2%A0In%20his%20complaint%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20has%20stated%20that%20he%20is%20not%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20BMW%20and%20does%20not%20own%20any%20illicit%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Soren%20had%20gone%20'missing'%20and%20the%20party's%20Jharkhand%20chief%2C%20Babulal%20Marandi%2C%20had%20also%20shared%20a%20poster%20seeking%20information%20about%20Mr%20Soren%20and%20announcing%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2011%2C000%20for%20information%20on%20his%20whereabouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%2C%20however%2C%20appeared%20in%20Ranchi%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20alleged%20that%20searching%20his%20home%20in%20his%20absence%20on%20Monday%20was%20%C2%A0%26quot%3Buncalled%20for%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunconstitutional%26quot%3B.%20His%20party%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20accepted%20Mr%20Soren's%20request%20to%20question%20him%20at%20his%20Ranchi%20home%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Maligning%20Community'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20refers%20to%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmember%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribe%26quot%3B%20and%20mentions%20a%20few%20people%20by%20name%20-%20%C2%A0Mr.%20Kapil%20Raj%2C%20Mr.%20Deovrat%20Jha%2C%20Mr.%20Anupam%20Kumar%2C%20Mr.%20Aman%20Patel%20-%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bunknown%20others%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ball%20officers%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%2C%20Ranchi%20Zonal%20Office%2C%20having%20their%20office%20at%20Hinoo%2C%20Ranchi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20the%20search%20operation%20at%20the%20Jharkhand%20Bhawan%20in%20New%20Delhi%20harassed%20and%20maligned%20him%20and%20his%20entire%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20said%20he%20was%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%20and%20found%20out%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20search%20was%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20premises.%20%26quot%3BThis%20purported%20search%20was%20without%20any%20notice%20to%20me%20nor%20was%20my%20presence%20required%20on%2029th%20January%202024%20at%20New%20Delhi%20by%20the%20abovenamed%20persons%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20in%20his%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20the%20abovenamed%20persons%20had%20required%20me%20to%20be%20present%20at%20Ranchi%20on%2029th%20and%2031%20January%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'BMW%20Not%20Mine'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20officers%20had%20leaked%20%26quot%3Bselective%20misinformation%26quot%3B%20that%20a%20blue%20BMW%20car%20seized%20from%20the%20premises%20was%20his%20and%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20illicit%20cash%20belonging%20to%20him%20had%20also%20been%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20car%20of%20BMW%20make%20which%20the%20abovenamed%20persons%20claim%20to%20have%20seized.%20I%20do%20not%20own%20any%20illicit%20cash.%20The%20abovenamed%20persons%20and%20unknown%20others%20who%20are%20not%20members%20of%20any%20Scheduled%20Caste%20or%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20have%20done%20the%20aforesaid%20acts%20intentionally%20to%20humiliate%20me%20in%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20alleged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20family%20members%20and%20I%20have%20suffered%20and%20experienced%20immense%20mental%2C%20psychological%20and%20emotional%20harm%20because%20of%20the%20acts%20committed%20by%20the%20above-named%20persons%20and%20unknown%20others%20who%20are%20not%20members%20of%20any%20SC%20or%20ST.%20I%20call%20upon%20you%20to%20register%20this%20FIR%20and%20take%20steps%20in%20accordance%20with%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706703240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0qbgi6i_hemant-soren_625x300_30_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv