anmar%20junta%20extends%20state%20of%20emergency%20on%20eve%20of%20coup%20anniversary%3A%20Military-run%20media%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706702227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107295394%2Cimgsize-46526.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmyanmar-junta-extends-state-of-emergency-on-eve-of-coup-anniversary-military-run-media%2Farticleshow%2F107295143.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107295143.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Myanmar's%20ruling%20junta%20reportedly%20prolonged%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20in%20the%20strife-ridden%20country%20for%20an%20additional%20six%20months%2C%20as%20per%20military-controlled%20media.%20Having%20seized%20power%20through%20a%20coup%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20military%20has%20consistently%20extended%20emergency%20rule.%20Reports%20indicated%20that%20the%20National%20Defence%20and%20Security%20Council%20of%20the%20country%20discussed%20the%20%26quot%3Bcurrent%20situation%26quot%3B%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20with%20unanimous%20support%20from%20all%20members%20for%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20state%20of%20emergency.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmyanmar-junta-extends-state-of-emergency-on-eve-of-coup-anniversary-military-run-media%2Farticleshow%2F107295143.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmyanmar-junta-extends-state-of-emergency-on-eve-of-coup-anniversary-military-run-media%2Famp_articleshow%2F107295143.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmyanmar-junta-extends-state-of-emergency-on-eve-of-coup-anniversary-military-run-media%2Famp_articleshow%2F107295143.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dutch%20Woman%2C%2028%2C%20Shares%20Final%20Post%20Before%20Being%20Euthanised%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2028-year-old%20woman%20from%20the%20Netherlands%20who%20documented%20her%20battle%20with%20myalgic%20encephalomyelitis%20(ME)%2C%20also%20known%20as%20CFS%20(chronic%20fatigue%20syndrome)%2C%20died%20on%20January%2027%2C%202024%2C%20after%20being%20euthanised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELauren%20Hoeve%20posted%20her%20final%20message%20on%20her%20blog%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhersenmist.wordpress.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ebrain%20fog%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E'%20on%20January%2024%20and%20she%20announced%20her%20last%20day%20would%20be%20Saturday%20(January%2027).%20She%20also%20posted%20a%20meme%20before%20being%20euthanised%20on%20her%20X%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20post%2C%20she%20thanked%20everyone%20who%20has%20been%20there%20for%20her%20during%20her%20illness%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20time%20before%20she%20announced%20her%20euthanasia%20wish.%20She%20informed%20her%20followers%20that%20her%20euthanasia%20would%20take%20place%20sometime%20on%20Saturday%20between%201%3A30%20pm%20and%202%3A30%20pm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20known%20each%20other%20long%20and%20well%20or%20only%20a%20little%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter.%20Through%20you%20all%2C%20I%20have%20felt%20less%20alone%2C%20and%20I%20am%20very%20grateful%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20don't%20wish%20me%20a%20good%20trip%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20was%20going%20on%20a%20trip%20(a%20beach%20holiday%20would%20be%20nice)...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20her%20final%20message%2C%20Lauren%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20chose%20to%20make%20the%20date%20and%20time%20public%20because%20you%20have%20all%20been%20so%20excited%20for%20this%20moment%20with%20me.%20I%20know%20from%20experience%20how%20supportive%20it%20can%20be%20to%20know%20when%20it%20is%20happening%20so%20that%20you%20can%20reflect%20on%20it%20for%20a%20moment%20or%20light%20a%20candle%20if%20you%20wish.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20will%20be%20my%20last%20tweet.%20Thanks%20for%20the%20love%2C%20everyone.%20I'm%20going%20to%20rest%20a%20bit%20more%20and%20be%20with%20my%20loved%20ones.%20Enjoy%20a%20last%20morbid%20meme%20from%20me.%20%E2%9D%A4%EF%B8%8F%F0%9F%98%8E%F0%9F%91%8D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNjtkQdvEvo%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FNjtkQdvEvo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Lauren%20%E2%9C%A8%20(%40dutchlauren)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdutchlauren%2Fstatus%2F1751186700313788636%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hoeve%20started%20documenting%20her%20application%20for%20euthanasia%20in%202022%20on%20her%20blog.%20She%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ME%20in%202019%2C%20and%20also%20has%20autism%2C%20anxiety%2C%20and%20ADHD%2C%20Mirror%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Hoeve's%20blog%2C%20she%20recounts%20that%20when%20she%20first%20told%20her%20GP%20about%20wanting%20to%20be%20voluntarily%20euthanised%2C%20he%20told%20her%20he%20respected%20her%20wishes%20but%20could%20not%20do%20it%20himself%20as%20her%20case%20was%20complex%20due%20to%20her%20psychological%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hoeve's%20was%20placed%20on%20the%20waiting%20list%20but%20her%20wait%20was%20longer%20than%20usual%20because%20of%20the%20pandemic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hoeve%20used%20to%20regularly%20update%20her%20followers%20about%20her%20health%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%20People%20used%20to%20send%20messages%20of%20encouragement%20and%20support.%20According%20to%20her%20profile%20on%20X%2C%20she%20described%20herself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bs