e.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20important%20discipline%20for%20me%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bbalanced%20lifestyle%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-68129595%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706782899868000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3MeHUGc4AOh9ndUsU2ryiS%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-68129595%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20revealed%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20tend%20to%20try%20and%20do%20some%20fasting%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20every%20week%20as%20part%20of%20a%20general%20balanced%20lifestyle%20but%20everyone%20will%20do%20this%20differently.%E2%80%9D%20Acknowledging%20a%20%E2%80%9Cweakness%E2%80%9D%20for%20sugary%20delights%2C%20he%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20means%20that%20I%20can%20then%20indulge%20myself%20in%20all%20the%20sugary%20treats%20I%20like%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20week.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20source%20close%20to%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20true%2C%20he%20doesn't%20eat%20anything%20at%20all%20on%20a%20Monday.%20It's%20remarkable%20really%2C%20given%20that%20he%20is%20often%20on%20visits%20or%20doing%20PMQ%20prep%20on%20a%20Monday.%20It's%20a%20real%20testament%20to%20the%20discipline%2C%20focus%2C%20and%20determination%20that%20he%20shows%20in%20all%20aspects%20of%20his%20life%20and%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20reported%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fself-controlled-sunak-eats-nothing-for-36-hours-a-week-mnxffxsb9%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706782899868000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2YtYGqwchJdCOlpDp7-A9S%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fself-controlled-sunak-eats-nothing-for-36-hours-a-week-mnxffxsb9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESunday%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20mentioned%20a%20preference%20for%20Mexican%20Coke%20because%20it%20is%20made%20with%20%26quot%3Bcane%20sugar%20rather%20than%20high%20fructose%20corn%20syrup.%26quot%3B%20He%20admitted%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20problem%20is%20I%20love%20sugary%20things.%20I%20eat%20a%20lot%20of%20sugary%20pastries%20and%20all%20the%20rest%20of%20it%20throughout%20the%20week.%20And%20I%20like%20my%20food.%20I%20don't%20exercise%20as%20much%20as%20I%20used%20to%20because%20of%20the%20job.%20So%20a%20little%20reset%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20week%2C%20a%20little%20detox.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20fasting%2036%20hours%20a%20week%20beneficial%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhile%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20weekly%20fasting%20might%20sound%20extreme%2C%20nutrition%20expert%20Adam%20Collins%20views%20it%20as%20a%20stricter%20version%20of%20the%20popular%205%3A2%20diet%2C%20where%20people%20limit%20themselves%20to%20500-600%20calories%20twice%20a%20week.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20add%20%5Bthe%20two%20days%5D%20together%2C%20it's%20pretty%20much%2036%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2F2024%2Fjan%2F29%2Ffasting-for-36-hours-the-experts-view-on-rishi-sunak-weekly-habit%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706782899868000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2O9PSsmiy8HQbu61ctApSc%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Flifeandstyle%2F2024%2Fjan%2F29%2Ffasting-for-36-hours-the-experts-view-on-rishi-sunak-weekly-habit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20Professor%20James%20Betts%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Bath%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20restricted%20calorie%20diet%2C%20unlike%20Mr%20Sunak's%2036-hour%20fasting%20approach%2C%20doesn't%20put%20the%20body%20into%20a%20fasted%20state.%20This%20means%20the%20body%20uses%20its%20normal%20energy%20stores.%20He%20explained%20that%20during%20Mr%20Sunak's%2036-hour%20fast%2C%20the%20body%20shifts%20from%20using%20carbohydrates%20for%20fuel%20to%20using%20fat.%20His%20research%20found%20that%20a%20more%20strict%20fast%20leads%20to%20a%20greater%20shift%20from%20burning%20carbs%20to%20using%20fat%2C%20though%20it%20comes%20with%20temporary%20glucose%20intolerance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20kind%20of%20fasting%20could%20promote%20%26quot%3Bmetabolic%20flexibility%2C%26quot%3B%20allowing%20the%20body%20to%20switch%20between%20fuel%20sources.%20Mr%20Collins%20suggested%20this%20might%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Bmetabolic%20resilience%2C%26quot%3B%20helping%20the%20body%20cope%20with%20modern%20diet%20and%20lifestyle%20pressures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFasting%20may%20also%20trigger%20autophagy%2C%20a%20cellular%20spring%20cleaning%20process.%20However%2C%20the%20claims%20about%20fasting's%20effects%2C%20including%20a%20longer%20life%2C%20are%20mostly%20based%20on%20animal%20research%20with%20longer%20fasts.%20While%20fasting%20might%20help%20in%20weight%20loss%2C%20it%20could%20have%20downsides%20like%20muscle%20loss%20and%20reduced%20physical%20activity%20due%20to%20lower%20energy%20levels%2C%20warned%20Mr%20Betts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20cognitive%20effects%20of%20fasting%20are%20uncertain.%20Although%20burning%20fat%20produces%20ketones%20linked%20to%20mental%20acuity%2C%20the%20benefits%20may%20not%20be%20significant%20after%20a%2036-hour%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Sunak's%20fasting%20isn't%20suitable%20for%20everyone%2C%20cautioned%20Adam%20Collins.%20It%20is%20not%20recommended%20for%20those%20with%20disordered%20eating%2C%20pregnant%20women%2C%20or%20thos