e%20based%20on%20the%20detection%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20presence.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20is%20compatible%20with%20Google%20Assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20freshener%20features%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fsustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiodegradable%20body%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20be%20composted%20after%20use%2C%20and%20its%20refills%20are%20organic%20%E2%80%94%20crafted%20from%20temple%20flower%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20nature%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20in%20retaining%20the%20fragrances.%20Chemical%20fresheners%20use%20LPG%20to%20retain%20the%20fragrance.%20We%20use%20natural%20ingredients%20for%20that%20with%20no%20chemicals.%20We%20do%20not%20use%20any%20heat%2C%20water%20vapour%20or%20chemicals%20to%20diffuse%20our%20fragrances.%20We%20use%20our%20own%20Air%20Diffusion%20Technology%20with%20sensors%20to%20diffuse%20aroma%20evenly%20in%20the%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20has%20partnered%20with%20more%20than%2030%20temples%20in%20Jamshedpur%20to%20obtain%20floral%20waste.%20Every%20day%2C%20he%20collects%20a%20minimum%20of%203%20kg%20of%20floral%20waste%20from%20each%20temple.%20To%20date%2C%20he%20has%20recycled%201%2C500%20kg%20of%20temple%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20noteworthy%20aspect%20is%20that%20this%20freshener%20is%20safe%20for%20animals%20also.%20Working%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20Animal%20Welfare%20Society%20since%202018%2C%20Rajiv%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20effects%20of%20human%20behaviour%20on%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rajiv%20made%20wheelchairs%20for%20dogs%