ay%20from%20the%20show%20for%20me%20has%20been%20the%20fact%20that%20young%20Indians%20are%20truly%20limitless.%20And%20they%20are%20from%20Tier%203%20and%204%20towns%20of%20the%20country.%20They%20are%20doing%20so%20much%20with%20limited%20resources%20and%20under%20difficult%20circumstances.%20I%E2%80%99m%20buoyed%20about%20finding%20young%20talent%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20everyone%20young%20or%20old%2C%20Radhika%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFind%20your%20sky%20and%20learn%20to%20fly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20world%20conspires%20to%20make%20you%20succeed%20if%20you%20want%20it%20hard%20enough.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20connect%20the%20dots%20but%20the%20dots%20start%20connecting.%20Each%20one%20of%20us%20is%20unique%20and%20different.%20Celebrate%20your%20perfections%20and%20imperfections%20and%20everything%20in%20between%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYour%20story%2C%20too%2C%20can%20have%20a%20happy%20ending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706076791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FGVZScZFGHVA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20being%20the%20'Girl%20With%20a%20Broken%20Neck'%20to%20selling%20her%20company%20to%20Edelweiss%20and%20becoming%20a%20judge%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%2C%20Radhika%20Gupta's%20journey%20has%20been%20truly%20incredible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A147%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339578%2Fradhika-gupta-shark-tank-india-judge-edelweiss-asset-management-broken-neck-ceo%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Man%20Takes%20Your%20Dry%20Waste%2C%20Recycles%20It%20%26amp%3B%20Gives%20You%20Rewards%20In%20Return!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWaste%20Management%20in%20India%2C%20particularly%20at%20the%20individual%20household%20level%2C%20has%20been%20a%20longstanding%20concern.%20Government%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.trade.gov%2Fmarket-intelligence%2Findia-solid-waste-management%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDue%2520to%2520rapid%2520urbanization%252C%2520economic%2Cof%2520waste%2520in%2520a%2520year.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimates%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%202021%20reveal%20that%20the%20country%20generates%20approximately%2062%20tonnes%20of%20Municipal%20Solid%20Waste%20(MSW)%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20this%20total%2C%2080%20percent%20is%20collected%2C%20but%20only%2022-28%20percent%20undergoes%20recycling.%20The%20remaining%20waste%20is%20deposited%20in%20landfills%2C%20contributing%20to%20additional%20environmental%20challenges.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffactly.in%2Freview-municipal-solid-waste-generated-in-india-set-to-increase-7-times-in-the-next-30-years%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCurrently%252C%2520as%2520per%2520government%2520estimates%2C%252C%2520wood%252C%2520glass%252C%2520etc.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReports%20%3C%2Fa%3Esuggest%20that%20the%20percentage%20of%20MSW%20is%20anticipated%20to%20surge%20by%20sevenfold%20in%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20issue%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20staggering%20figures%20underscore%20the%20critical%20problem%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332607%2Fkerala-pharma-scientist-kenterra-low-cost-solution-waste-management-compost-apartment-complex%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20segregation%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20micro%20level.%20Records%20indicate%20that%20a%20mere%2030%20percent%20of%20waste%20undergoes%20proper%20segregation%2C%20leading%20to%20recyclable%20materials%20like%20plastic%20being%20wrongly%20disposed%20of%20in%20landfills%2C%20where%20they%20contribute%20to%20environmental%20degradation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20believe%20is%20that%20people%20need%20some%20kind%20of%20incentive%20to%20do%20something.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20concept%20where%20people%20get%20a%20reward%20for%20segregating%20their%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek%20Agarwal%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Goodeebag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoodeebag%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20waste%20management%20company%2C%20collects%20your%20segregated%20waste%20from%20your%20doorstep%20and%20provides%20reward%20points%20in%20return.%20Users%20can%20redeem%20these%20reward%20points%20to%20purchase%20groceries%20from%20the%20Goodeebag%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20icing%20on%20the%20top%3F%20All%20these%20services%20are%20free%20of%20cost!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOne%20man%E2%80%99s%20waste%20is%20another%E2%80%99s%20treasure%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20typical%20Marwari%20family%2C%20Abhishek%20claims%20that%20business%20is%20in%20his%20blood.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20entire%20family%20is%20full%20of%20successful%20businessmen%20in%20various%20fields%2C%20so%20for%20me%2C%20I%20had%20always%20known%20that%20entrepreneurship%20was%20my%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-1706017585.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20and%20recycled%20over%2089%2C164%20kg%20of%20waste%20so%20far.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-1706017585.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-1706017585-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-170